  2	 * Build script for liminal-spec skill pack.
  3	 *
  4	 * Reads manifest.json, composes markdown source files into self-contained
  5	 * skill output files, and packages for distribution.
  6	 *
  7	 * Output structure:
  8	 *   dist/skills/{name}/SKILL.md              -- YAML frontmatter + composed content
  9	 *   dist/skills/{name}/references/*.md       -- Optional bundled companion guides
 10	 *   dist/standalone/{name}-skill.md          -- Frontmatter-stripped single skill markdown
 11	 *   dist/standalone/liminal-spec-skill-pack.zip
 12	 *   dist/standalone/liminal-spec-markdown-pack.zip
 13	 *
 14	 * Optional environment variables:
 15	 *   DIST_DIR -- output root directory (default: dist)
 16	 */
